Natural hazards:
Typhoons, earthquakes, and severe flooding are quite rare, but Brunei is located along the Pacific Ring of Fire.

Environment - current issues:
seasonal smoke/haze resulting from forest fires in <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a>

Environment - international agreements:
