<a href="Agence%20de%20Coop%C3%A9ration%20Culturelle%20et%20Technique">ACCT</a>, <a href="ACP%20%28Lom%C3%A9%20Convention%29">ACP</a>, <a href="AfDB">AfDB</a>, <a href="African%20Union">AU</a>, <a href="United%20Nations%20Economic%20Commission%20for%20Africa">ECA</a>, <a href="Economic%20Community%20of%20West%20African%20States">ECOWAS</a>, <a href="Conseil%20de%20l%27Entente">Entente</a>, <a href="Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organization">FAO</a>, <a href="Group%20of%2077">G-77</a>, <a href="International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency">IAEA</a>, <a href="World%20Bank">IBRD</a>, <a href="International%20Civil%20Aviation%20Organization">ICAO</a>, <a href="International%20Criminal%20Court">ICC</a>, <a href="International%20Trade%20Union%20Confederation">ITUC</a>, <a href="International%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Movement">ICRM</a>, <a href="International%20Development%20Association">IDA</a>, <a href="Islamic%20Development%20Bank">IDB</a>, <a href="International%20Fund%20for%20Agricultural%20Development">IFAD</a>, <a href="International%20Finance%20Corporation">IFC</a>, <a href="International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies">IFRCS</a>, <a href="International%20Labour%20Organization">ILO</a>, <a href="International%20Monetary%20Fund">IMF</a>, <a href="Intelsat">Intelsat</a>, <a href="Interpol%20%28organization%29">Interpol</a>, <a href="International%20Olympic%20Committee">IOC</a>, <a href="International%20Telecommunication%20Union">ITU</a>, <a href="Non-Aligned%20Movement">NAM</a>, <a href="Organization%20of%20African%20Unity">OAU</a>, <a href="Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation">OIC</a>, <a href="Organisation%20for%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Chemical%20Weapons">OPCW</a>, <a href="Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration">PCA</a>, <a href="United%20Nations">UN</a>, <a href="United%20Nations%20Conference%20on%20Trade%20and%20Development">UNCTAD</a>, <a href="United%20Nations%20Educational%2C%20Scientific%20and%20Cultural%20Organization">UNESCO</a>, <a href="United%20Nations%20Industrial%20Development%20Organization">UNIDO</a>, <a href="Universal%20Postal%20Union">UPU</a>, <a href="West%20African%20Development%20Bank">WADB</a>, WADB (regional), <a href="WAEMU">WAEMU</a>, <a href="World%20Customs%20Organization">WCO</a>, <a href="World%20Federation%20of%20Trade%20Unions">WFTU</a>, <a href="World%20Health%20Organization">WHO</a>, <a href="World%20Intellectual%20Property%20Organization">WIPO</a>, <a href="World%20Meteorological%20Organization">WMO</a>, <a href="World%20Tourism%20Organization">WToO</a>, <a href="World%20Trade%20Organization">WTrO</a>

The ambassador of Burkina Faso to Canada is <a href="Juliette%20Bonkoungou">Juliette Bonkoungou</a>.

The ambassador of Burkina Faso to Mexico is Jonathan Hodgson

The former ambassador of Burkina Faso to the United States was <a href="Tertius%20Zongo">Tertius Zongo</a>, he left his post when appointed Prime Minister in July 2007; the US Ambassador to Burkina Faso is Tulinabo Mushingi.


